Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:19.93,Song,,0,0,0,,If only there were no tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:23.66,Song,,0,0,0,,School would've been a fun place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:30.00,Song,,0,0,0,,I never cared much for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:38.52,Song,,0,0,0,,I just stared out the window all through class,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:44.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}Always dreaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:52.50,Song,,0,0,0,,But if I'd at least taken English seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:59.81,Song,,0,0,0,,By now I'd be some cool international girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.77,0:01:07.38,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study a little than not at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:12.92,Song,,0,0,0,,There must be at least one thing you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.52,0:01:22.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study while you still have the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:28.17,Song,,0,0,0,,Realizing too late won't help you then.
