Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,An in-school lacrosse tournament. {meaning its students will play against its other students}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.94,0:01:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A form-on-form? {??? lit: grade rivalry - assuming it means "one grade vs another grade" although could be that they'll just split one form into two teams?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.11,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, start practising for the lacrosse \Ntournament from today.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.48,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hilary, please go sort out \Nthe field schedule at lunchtime.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.70,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Patricia?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.06,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the lacrosse tournament \Nbetween the forms?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.16,0:02:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, the seniors are bound to win. {that answers my question ig}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s what I think too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless there’s some sort of handicap...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we’ll never stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.87,0:02:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s not always the seniors who win, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.29,0:02:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.54,0:02:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, this tournament is meant \Nto bring pupils together and foster teamwork.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning and losing isn’t everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.22,0:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s why everyone is required to take part.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.15,0:02:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it’s only a week away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.79,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Practise hard and enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, twins.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you just can’t rest easy \Nwithout grumbling about something. {referring to them complaining that the seniors will win}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But sport is only fun if you play to win!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! If you give up \Nfrom the start it’s no fun at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.71,0:02:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then, we’ll just have to win no matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Janet?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.10,0:03:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan! Sheila’s running for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.54,0:03:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, \Nputting it in our own goal?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.51,0:03:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Joan, get a grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your passing still isn’t good enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll work on that from tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who isn’t handy \Nwith their stick had better practise.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.04,0:04:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan, I don’t ask you to score, \Nbut at least don’t help the other side score!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.58,0:04:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m not playing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone must take part—it’s the rule.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.42,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind who wins or loses.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s just take it easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.76,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m more looking forward \Nto the tea party afterwards.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see? I managed a pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it. Well done!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.17,0:04:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Even I can do it when I try.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've barely started, \Nbut she's already given up trying.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And the others don’t seem to be trying either.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll never win at this rate.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you give up already?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.12,0:04:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I’ll train Joan myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Train me?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.63,0:04:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you practise every day, \Nyou’ll improve before the match, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.13,0:04:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I’ll help too, with Kathleen.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.47,0:05:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your stick higher!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.37,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.60,0:05:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.77,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.38,0:05:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan! The ball won’t bite. \NKeep your eyes on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.31,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go! There!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.39,0:05:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan! Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.23,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s enough, I’m just no good at sports.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it’s anything to boast of, \Nbut I always come in last in P.T.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan, they're still offering refills.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? That’s unusual.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.43,0:06:08.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,I always make a mess of it when it really matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,I hate matches.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.37,Thought,,0,0,0,,Why must I play no matter what?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.54,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your leg quite all right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can run and jump again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.46,0:06:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I fell off the stage set, it hurt dreadfully—\NI thought for certain I’d broken a bone.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been awful.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.35,0:06:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I’m glad it was nothing serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.73,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish all our P.T. lessons were lacrosse just now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.38,0:06:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! With only three days left, \Nwe ought to practise more.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I should really like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.14,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a rare sight—\NJoan's climbed onto the balance beam!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.69,0:07:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... My leg!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts too badly!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.55,0:07:25.68,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get her to Matron, quickly!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.12,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to fret; a poultice \Nand she’ll be better by tomorrow, no doubt.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But I... Ow-ow-ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt so badly?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.01,0:07:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that’s serious! You might need to go into the town infirmary, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.98,0:08:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh no, it’s not such dreadful pain, \Nbut I don’t think I can walk for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case I’ll give you some special medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.86,0:08:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminds me—I once gave this same drug \Nto another pupil often enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.86,0:08:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name was Felicia, if I remember aright.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Miss Roberts?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a plumpish girl, rather like Joan, \Nand not keen on games.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She particularly detested lacrosse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.81,0:08:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before P.T. she would often complain of stomach-aches,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.64,0:08:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I dosed her with this medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicia’s great friend was Judy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.53,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Judy had a weak leg, \Nso she never played games, only watched.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them were thick as thieves.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.99,0:08:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But one day Felicia...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,caught sight of Judy secretly practising lacrosse.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.36,0:08:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,With her bad leg?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.37,0:08:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. But of course Judy couldn’t manage it, \Nand she was bitterly vexed.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.02,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“If only my leg were sound, \NI’d prove myself good at it!” she cried.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When Felicia heard that, \Nit struck her like a blow.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.58,0:09:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She realised how shameful it was \Nto have a sound body and not use it.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.92,0:09:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,From that very day, \NFelicia began daily practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.59,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard labour, indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.18,0:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to it, she grew skilful—\Nnot only at lacrosse but at other sports too.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.56,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How splendid!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.03,0:09:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was another benefit to it as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicia soon became quite slim.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the situation is settled now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to class. \NI’ll see to the rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.12,0:09:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Joan?\NWant to sit out P.T.?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.39,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose I could ever \Ngrow good at lacrosse too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.86,0:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan, human beings are curious creatures.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.47,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With effort and practice, \None improves little by little at anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.11,0:10:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even at things one dislikes?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.81,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, talent and disposition \Ndo have their place,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.24,0:10:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but until you try, you can't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.45,0:10:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you just convinced yourself \Nyou're no good?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.45,0:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I think... I'd rather...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.69,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No pianist, however great, \Nbegan by playing Mozart or Chopin.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.78,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to test your own powers is sheer loss. \NDon't you think, Joan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.25,0:10:51.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,To possess a sound body \Nand never use it—that is shameful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.12,0:10:52.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,Human beings are curious creatures.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.92,0:10:57.46,Thought,,0,0,0,,With effort and practice, \None improves little by little at anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.46,0:11:01.24,Thought,,0,0,0,,Not to test your own powers is sheer loss.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, one, two, one, two, one, two!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.81,0:11:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Joan. \NIs your leg better?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.71,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! A-And, er...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.18,0:11:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm practising as well. We mistresses will have a match too. Want to do it together?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.20,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nearly there, Joan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.11,0:11:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the ball a touch earlier \Nand try your shot again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Told you, it's Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? And Miss Roberts too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.12,0:12:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! That timing's just right, Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.03,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, next, receive the pass and take your shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.16,0:12:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.03,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts rose early \Njust for Joan, didn’t she?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I daresay so.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.74,0:12:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thought Miss Roberts was too strict, \Nbut she’s more complex than that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.04,0:12:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She can be quite a considerate person too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go, Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.16,0:12:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So close! Once more!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.99,0:12:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.99,0:12:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we have a good match \Nthe day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.61,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall now decide the match-ups. \NRepresentatives of each form, please gather.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.02,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Never fear, Joan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.54,0:13:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You today are not the Joan of a few days ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have confidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.46,0:13:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! \NOur first match is against the Fifth Form.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Belinda's form?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To be drawn against the favourites, of all things!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.85,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lousy luck! \NWe shan’t stand a chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.24,0:13:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, all of you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not yet know we shall lose.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.61,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. One must never \Nthrow a match from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.23,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is by playing the strong teams \Nthat one gains skill.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.25,0:13:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we lose, there is much to learn \Nif we apply ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite so!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let’s do our best \Nand have a good game.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.93,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s the spirit!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.90,0:13:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And one never knows \Nwhat may happen in a match.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.78,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.83,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us all show them our overwhelming vigour!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.22,0:13:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well said!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.16,0:13:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.80,0:13:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.67,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s give it our all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.34,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The starting members and positions \Nare as decided yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First Home, Patricia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.32,0:14:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Home, Isabel.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.12,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.62,0:14:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Home, Vera.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.72,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.15,0:14:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right Attack Wing, Janet!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.89,0:14:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.62,0:14:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The first round \Nis Fifth Form against First Form.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.06,0:14:24.00,Top,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare lose to the freshmen!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.60,Top,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kathleen?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.26,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. But what a shot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of Belinda.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.05,0:15:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alison! Pass!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Tess! {?????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.18,0:15:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Belinda!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.51,0:15:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Belinda is just too formidable.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.59,0:15:21.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,Whenever the ball comes her way, \Nshe always intercepts it.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.20,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let Belinda run freely! \NTry to get in her way! {???????? can't hear shit}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.40,0:15:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Substitution! {/member change}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.46,0:15:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Janet, get on the field. {/change}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.57,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now’s our chance!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts says, while Belinda’s absent, \Ngo in and intercept everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Everyone, let’s do our best!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.53,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{dont care anymore}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.32,0:16:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Halftime! {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.13,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Delightful!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.91,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of the twins, \Nyou’re so well-coordinated!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up that spirit and stay sharp.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We're already sharp! {/doing our best}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.89,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re finding our stride now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the match around in the {ten minutes of the }second half. {really not sure how that's supposed to work, no way the match is only 20 minutes, right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.21,0:16:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is Belinda.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.11,0:16:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We must mark her closely \Nand keep their goals to a minimum. {lost point (in a game); point given away; conceded goal}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.33,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could just stay here \Nand not have to go out to play.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Attagirl, Isabel!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to Alison!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.23,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, four minutes remaining!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s give it our all!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan, switch with Vera.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? M-Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.77,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's hopeless.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.90,0:17:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just follow the practice—\Nreceive the pass, then shoot.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pat, Isabel, go get them!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.02,0:18:24.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,As practised... \NAs practised, when the ball comes...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.93,0:18:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.93,0:18:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.93,0:18:33.42,Thought,,0,0,0,,As practised...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.82,0:18:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.42,0:18:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Joan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.82,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it go in?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! It’s all square. {equal score}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now we take the lead! {/turn it around}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.35,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.32,0:19:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No time left! \NJust one more point!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.80,0:19:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth Form versus First Form, 18 to 17, Fifth Form victorious.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,'Twas a splendid match.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.52,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A fine shot! I never knew we had \Nsuch a strong point-getter in our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call—we almost lost!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.53,0:20:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifth Form! Keep going!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.68,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We shan’t forgive you if you lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Belinda, shoot!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, the Fifth Form are champions!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.36,0:20:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After matching the champions blow for blow,\Ndon't you think we deserve second place?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.30,0:20:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, Janet is only here \Nfor the accolades! {?? not sure what she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.64,0:20:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The champions: Fifth Form.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.36,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not have won, \Nbut it was a match of far greater value.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.98,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Joan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite so.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.89,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, an exhibition match between \Nthe victorious Fifth Form and the staff team.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.46,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please cheer them on.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Headmistress is playing too?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.57,0:21:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be hard to tell now, \Nbut I was once lacrosse captain. Watch and see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.24,0:21:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Joan, I was watching it closely.\NYou were fabulous.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.88,0:21:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I finally gained confidence, \Nthanks to you and all the other mistresses.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.48,0:21:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And most of all, I wish I could thank Felicia \Nfor showing me what I am truly capable of. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can. {thank her}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.59,0:21:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, there she is—Felicia Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.67,0:21:53.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can scarcely believe strict Miss Roberts \Nhad such a childhood.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.08,0:22:00.02,Thought,,0,0,0,,She truly wished to share \Nher own experiences with Joan and us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.02,0:22:02.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,To teach us the importance of effort!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Felicia, fight!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.76,0:22:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts, do your best!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.25,0:22:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Roberts!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.88,0:23:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, Binks has run away \Nfrom Kathleen’s house!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.19,0:23:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That Binks... He ran all the way \Nto St. Clare's to see Kathleen.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:44.89,0:23:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But the rules forbid you to keep pets here!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.59,0:23:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules this, rules that—\Nit’s seriously tiresome!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.36,0:23:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No one may keep Binks but Kathleen. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.23,0:23:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so a grand debate \Non the subject of rules was held in class.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.50,0:23:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twins at St. Clare's:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.04,0:24:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"All-Night Debate!" {朝まで討論会!}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.29,0:24:03.73,Note,,0,0,0,,Episode 16 \NAll-Night Debate! {朝まで討論会!}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.51,0:24:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do look forward to it!
